data.description: Spacious Spanish style home on nearly 1-1/2 acres w/spectacular mtn views & over 5100SF finished space. Upper features 4 large bdrms, full bath & office-3 bdrms have private balconies. Master & 1 other bdrm have private bas & walkin closets. Formal living & dining areas + cozy main level familyroom. Huge bsmt has add'l FP, recroom, exercise room w/sauna & 5th non-conforming bdrm. Definite need for updating but great opportunity for sweat equity. Home is being sold "as as" & is priced accordingly
